            <title>[SOLR-16231] Fix ref-guide links across the codebase</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-16231</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;As of 9.0, the Solr ref guide has moved to Antora, and all of our ref-guide page URLs have changed.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We have successfully created redirects for most of the page links, but we should use the new and correct versions in the codebase.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
