                            <comment id="17558190" author="houston" created="Thu, 23 Jun 2022 18:31:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;As referenced in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-16237&quot; title=&quot;Broken link to reference guide on index.html for Query Syntax and Parsers&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-16237&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-16237&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, Solr 9.0.0 was released with many links that were made for the new (or renamed) 9.0 pages. These links were not updated to use the new ref guide format. When we made redirects to map the old versionless ref-guide pages to the new antora URLs, these links were not included because they didn&apos;t exist in the 8_11 ref guide release. So now we need to include redirects for them as well.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
